comments: Replay review of the foul called on Davis (LAL) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Davis makes contact to Valanciunas' (NOP) arm that affects his shot attempt in the post.
James (LAL) jumps and releases the pass before returning to the floor.
Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bradley (LAL) and does not deliver contact.
Bradley (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by McCollum (NOP).
Jones (NOP) makes contact with the backboard during Westbrook's (LAL) shot attempt, but does not cause the ball to take an unnatural bounce.
Jones (NOP) briefly places a marginal hand on Westbrook's (LAL) body that does not affect his shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Ingram (NOP) makes contact to James' (LAL) head/face that affects his driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAL) initiates marginal contact with Ingram (NOP) prior to his jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAL) commits a take foul on McCollum (NOP).
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Jones (NOP) and does not deliver contact.
